title: Listening for Aliens, with Carolyn Porco - StarTalk All-Stars
description: Explore SETI and the Breakthrough Listen Initiative, the most comprehensive search for extraterrestrial intelligence ever, with host Carolyn Porco, co-host Chuck Nice, and Dan Werthimer, the Initiative’s principal investigator and SETI@home co-founder.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
